WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:14.680 --> 00:00:42.640
 Ingredients: 1 kg of flour - 700 g of soft butter - 250 g of icing sugar - dried fruits: 

00:00:42.640 --> 00:00:53.160
 hazelnuts - ground sesame - almonds - and sesame seeds for decoration 

00:00:54.540 --> 00:01:01.300
 salt - paper molds to put the ghraiba 

00:01:05.520 --> 00:01:12.660
 in a terrine put the 700 g of soft butter 

00:01:14.440 --> 00:01:20.640
 add 250 g icing sugar 

00:01:21.860 --> 00:01:29.220
 and mix well 

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:43.740
 we get this mixture of sugar butter 

00:01:44.140 --> 00:01:50.500
 we add the ground sesame 

00:01:50.500 --> 00:01:56.680
 we blend 

00:01:56.680 --> 00:02:02.380
 a pinch of salt is added to the flour 

00:02:04.820 --> 00:02:27.440
 and add the sugar butter flour gradually 

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:35.560
 and we mix 

00:03:05.200 --> 00:03:11.060
 soft and soft dough should be obtained 

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:19.040
 we add the ground hazelnuts 

00:03:19.040 --> 00:03:23.620
 and ground almonds 

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:30.700
 and we mix 

00:04:12.260 --> 00:04:19.260
 we prepare the paper molds that will receive the ghraiba 

00:04:20.300 --> 00:04:32.260
 we make balls that we put in the molds 

00:04:32.260 --> 00:04:51.440
 we decorate with sesame seeds 

00:05:23.500 --> 00:05:29.240
 the oven is heated 

00:05:35.580 --> 00:05:42.340
 and for cooking the ghraiba we lower the temperature 

00:05:42.340 --> 00:05:49.580
 the cooking time must not exceed 15 minutes 

00:05:56.060 --> 00:06:15.040
 after cooking 

00:06:17.020 --> 00:06:23.760
 Enjoy your meal and see you soon 

